vote.title: A resolution authorizing the conveyance of an easement and right of way containing approximately 5,624 square feet of land to Oncor Electric Delivery Company, LLC for the construction, maintenance and use of power lines and electric transformer facilities across City-owned land located at the intersection of Luther and Keeler Streets - Financing : No cost consideration to the City
